      "time": "~20s",
      "narrative": "Now we step back from the finished application and show how the agent work started. This is a proof of concept in the GitHub Copilot app, running locally with local or simulated data. It is useful because it lets us test the invoice review task early, before we harden anything for production.",
      "demo_actions": "Open the GitHub Copilot app. Briefly orient the viewer to the environment and call out that this is a local or simulated POC.",
