      "time": "~30s",
      "narrative": "Inside the project, the working areas are where the POC comes together. Chat helps us steer the task, rubber duck helps us reason through it, actions shows runnable steps, agent merge manages changes, and canvas is where the agent itself takes shape.",
      "demo_actions": "Show the project-level areas: chat, rubber duck, actions, agent merge, and canvas. Briefly point out each pane.",
