        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~40s",
      "narrative": "When we run it, the agent can approximate the same reasoning path we want in Waypoint. It checks local or simulated contracts, receipts, batch records, quality status, milestone approvals, and invoice lines, then returns a recommendation with supporting evidence.",
      "demo_actions": "Run the agent on a sample invoice. Show inputs, tool or record access, and the resulting recommendation with cited evidence.",
